01:05:41,130 --> 01:05:43,060
<font color="yellow"><i>[Dear My Friends]</i></font>

803
01:05:43,390 --> 01:05:45,670
<font color="yellow"><i>Aku tidak bisa tidur.</i></font>

804
01:05:45,670 --> 01:05:47,360
<font color="yellow"><i>Ibu./
Siapa itu?</i></font>

805
01:05:48,330 --> 01:05:49,580
<font color="yellow"><i>Kita akan bertemu di gereja.</i></font>

806
01:05:49,580 --> 01:05:51,500
<font color="yellow"><i>Aku ganti baju dulu.</i></font>

807
01:05:51,500 --> 01:05:53,500
<font color="yellow"><i>Berteman saja. Jangan
selalu pergi dengannya.</i></font>

808
01:05:53,500 --> 01:05:55,230
<font color="yellow"><i>Aku harusnya yang ada disana.</i></font>

809
01:05:55,660 --> 01:05:58,460
<font color="yellow"><i>Mereka saling menyukai.
Relakan saja.</i></font>

810
01:05:59,190 --> 01:06:01,190
<font color="yellow"><i>Kau sungguh merindukanku?</i></font>

811
01:06:02,060 --> 01:06:03,320
<font color="yellow"><i>Kenapa kau tiba-tiba jadi baik?</i></font>

812
01:06:03,320 --> 01:06:05,590
<font color="yellow"><i>Aku baik karena kita tidak
punya banyak waktu lagi.</i></font>

813
01:06:06,230 --> 01:06:09,030
<font color="yellow"><i>Aku harus pergi, 'kan?</i></font>

814
01:06:09,830 --> 01:06:12,360
<font color="yellow"><i>Jika kau tidak datang,
aku akan bunuh diri.</i></font>

